description:
VB.NET source file that contains an abstract base class called "LicenseInfo" that is used by various concrete licenses implementations and also by the AcknowledgementAttribute.

Do not install this package manually, as it is installed automatically through referencing NuGet packages where needed.

Supported versions:
.NET Framework 2.0
.NET Framework 3.0
.NET Framework 3.5
.NET Framework 3.5 Client Profile
.NET Framework 4.0
.NET Framework 4.0 Client Profile
.NET Framework 4.5
.NET Framework 4.5.1
.NET Framework 4.5.2
.NET Framework 4.6
.NET Framework 4.6.1

This package is part of the SingleFile.VB collection.

Your feedback and/or contribution is welcome. Please contact me on "singlefile.vb@gmail.com".
